						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Broken stone near the Kallēśvara temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged record mentions a member (name lost) of <hi rend="bold">Māṭūra</hi> family who is described as the lord of Trikundapura. It seems to record a grant of land. The characters belong to about the <hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.</hi></p>						

